* decline in India's foreign exchange reserves which may affect liquidity in the Indian economy;
* downgrading of India's sovereign debt rating by rating agencies;
* difficulty in developing any necessary partnerships with local businesses on commercially acceptable terms and/or a timely basis.
* changes in India's tax, trade, fiscal or monetary policies; and
* other significant regulatory or economic developments in or affecting India or its logistics sector.
